2001-06-13  proff_fs
	* src/m_fixed.h:
	* src/m_fixed.h:
		fixed NOASM targets in VisualC++

2001-06-09  cph
	* src/r_draw.c:
		Rewrite R_DrawSpan without the single-position-register optimisation;
		a span can be as long as 1024 pixels in PrBoom so we need far more than
		10 bits precision for fractional steps. Only way to do that is to use
		separate registers for X and Y stepping. This cures a lot of interference
		and distortions on close up flats, and should cure "jumpiness" of flats
		under flickering light.

	* src/p_map.c:
		Remove some unused cruft

2001-05-26  cph
	* NEWS:
	* configure.in:
	* src/g_game.c:
	* src/p_mobj.c:
		Bump version number
		Improve lost soul bouncing demo fix - restores sync in many Doom 1 demos
		 and improves Doom 2 sync
		Fix fastparm and respawnparm loading from save games
		Update NEWS file

2001-05-19  cph
	* acconfig.h:
	* config.h:
	* configure.in:
	* src/doomdata.h:
	* src/doomstat.h:
	* src/m_misc.c:
	* src/p_spec.c:
	* src/p_spec.h:
	* src/r_data.c:
