2000-10-15  proff_fs
	* src/Drawasm.nas:
		Fixed naming of assembler functions

2000-10-10  cph
	* src/SDL/i_video.c:
	* src/drawcol.S:
	* src/drawspan.S:
	* src/r_data.c:
	* src/r_draw.c:
	* src/r_draw.h:
		R_Draw(TL)?Column is no longer a pointer to a choice of "Normal" (read:
		old 320x200) or "Highres". We're back to the simple arrangement of
		a single R_DrawColumn and R_DrawTLColumn, which are the highres
		versons. General cleanup of related bits.

