2000-05-15  proff_fs
	* src/gl_intern.h:
	* src/gl_main.c:
	* src/gl_texture.c:
	* src/r_bsp.c:
		reworked texture managment. added scaling to textures.
		ifdefed scaling and mipmaping of textures.
		gld_max_texturesize is now used, that means that
		Voodoo-Cards should work now
		added another method to triangulate flats. this fixes unclosed
		sectors and makes use with mesa possible. problems are
		small gaps between subsectors.
		ifdefed gluTesselator for mesa.
		fixed some textureposition bugs
		fixed wall y-position bug
		possibly other fixes

