	* configure.in:
		Add OpenGL configure option
		Add configure option for profiling

	* configure.in:
		When compiling for OpenGL don't compile X target

	* src/Makefile.am:
		Include gl_* source files when compiling with OpenGL

	* src/v_video.h:
		Fix compile problems, gl_struct.h must follow enum patch_translation_e
		definition

	* src/p_enemy.h:
		Minor additions from PrBoom

